node.title: Police launch homicide inquiry after death of woman in her 60s
node.description: The death of a woman who was found at a property in Christchurch is being treated as a homicide.
node.content:
["Christchurch police are now treating the death of a woman in her 60s in the Christchurch suburb of Woolston as a homicide.", "", "
File pic Photo: 123rf
", "Detective Senior Sergeant Nicola Reeves said police are continuing to examine a property in Walcot Street where the woman's body was found on Monday evening.", "A post-mortem has been carried out.", "Reeves said police are making inquiries into how the woman died.", "They do not intend releasing her name at present."]
